text:
にるしあ：
中国語が話せる方を代表してお詫び申し上げます。当時、多くの中国語話者がチャットルームの品質を悪意を持って傷つけていました。チャットルームの質が悪いことをお詫び申し上げます。誤解しないでください。あなたを好きな人はまだたくさんいます。私たちは彼らとは異なります。私の日本語はあまり上手ではありませんので、ご不便をおかけしましたらご容赦ください。

text:
Global result (Except the last 4 races due to Exhibition Match) 
Holofantasy: 297 — Holoforce: 283

I can feel both generations and how work they...
Holofantasy works too synchronized, like more than family. Everyone has facilities. 
Holoforce gives that non-official name due to same working style, but all force radicates on one of their members (Obviously Coco-kaichou) 

This is one of last Coco-kaichou's collabs... Despite all 4th Generation remain members will be united after Coco-kaichou's graduation, Holoforce (4th Generation, of course) will not be the same thing.

For Rushia, if she's reading: Please take care of this material with love.
